Package: ros-jade-depth-image-proc
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libboost-all-dev, ros-jade-cv-bridge, ros-jade-eigen-conversions, ros-jade-image-geometry, ros-jade-image-transport, ros-jade-nodelet, ros-jade-tf2, ros-jade-tf2-ros
Description: Contains nodelets for processing depth images such as those produced by OpenNI camera.
 Functions include creating disparity images and point clouds, as well as registering (reprojecting) a depth image into another camera frame.
